1
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:56,040
Master of the Soul Lamp, this is the place.

2
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,950
This is the secret realm you left behind back then.

3
00:00:57,950 --> 00:01:00,950
Only the spiritual power of your Soul Lamp can open it.

4
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:17,039
You guys enter the secret realm first.

5
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:18,170
I'll cover the rear.

6
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:20,840
Go in first. Don't cause trouble for him.

7
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:27,980
Close the door.

8
00:01:35,539 --> 00:01:36,700
You say you're fine,

9
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:39,910
but blood has soaked through two layers of clothing.

10
00:01:39,910 --> 00:01:41,039
This little scratch

11
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,160
is nothing.

12
00:01:52,539 --> 00:01:53,789
What are you looking at?

13
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:55,160
I just didn't want this kid's

14
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:57,000
blood to attract demons.

15
00:01:57,750 --> 00:01:59,160
Ying, thank you.

16
00:01:59,330 --> 00:02:00,160
Cut the crap.

17
00:02:15,370 --> 00:02:17,370
Ying's past,

18
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:18,950
can you tell me about it?

19
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,700
A thousand years ago, the Creator God sacrificed himself for the world,

20
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:26,660
forged the Soul Lamp,

21
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:27,910
and split his divine soul in two.

22
00:02:27,910 --> 00:02:28,540
He sealed them into the lamp,

23
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:29,700
and thus we were born.

24
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:30,790
You manage salvation

25
00:02:30,790 --> 00:02:31,700
and are revered by millions.

26
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,000
I manage suppressing evil,

27
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:35,200
bearing all the world's malice for you.

28
00:02:35,329 --> 00:02:37,000
People treat me as a disaster-bringing evil spirit

29
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,000
and hunt me down everywhere.

30
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,500
But back then, you clearly knew

31
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:41,040
I had never harmed anyone.

32
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,250
Yet, high upon the altar,

33
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,450
in front of the whole world,

34
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:50,790
you personally locked me in the dark Land of Chaos.

35
00:02:52,370 --> 00:02:54,329
Until the war between humans and demons three hundred years ago,

36
00:02:54,329 --> 00:02:56,829
I sensed through the seal that your life was hanging by a thread.

37
00:02:56,829 --> 00:02:58,579
Risking my soul scattering,

38
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:00,620
I broke the seal to find you.

39
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:03,160
Why did you abandon me?

40
00:03:06,330 --> 00:03:07,910
A-Ying, don't be afraid.

41
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:10,330
I will definitely find a way to break the array

42
00:03:10,330 --> 00:03:11,200
and save you.

43
00:03:13,620 --> 00:03:16,579
Today, in the name of the Master of the Soul Lamp,

44
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:17,829
I seal it.

45
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:31,579
Hmph.

46
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:40,700
A-Ying, that's not true.

47
00:03:42,450 --> 00:03:44,410
It's never been what you thought.

48
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,040
I never wanted to abandon you.

49
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:49,950
Your origin divine soul was slowly being devoured and dispersing.

50
00:03:49,950 --> 00:03:51,410
Even your aura was fading.

51
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:54,000
I searched all the ancient texts left by the Creator God.

52
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,700
Only the sealing array in the Land of Chaos could

53
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,250
lock the out-of-control power in your body

54
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:58,329
and mend your soul.

55
00:03:58,329 --> 00:04:00,130
That was the only way to save you.

56
00:04:01,370 --> 00:04:02,790
Shortly after the sealing,

57
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:05,790
the war between humans and demons suddenly broke out.

58
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:07,330
A-Ying.

59
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,950
I'm sorry.

60
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:16,620
I desperately broke the seal to find you,

61
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:19,350
not to watch you throw your life away for a mortal.

62
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:27,720
But I couldn't let you go after all.

63
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:30,360
Also, back in Luoxia Village,

64
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:31,540
I didn't swallow living souls.

65
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:33,400
That was just a lie to deceive you.

66
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,159
I'm sorry, A-Ying.

67
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:45,250
Only by staying far away from me

68
00:04:46,580 --> 00:04:48,159
can you live well.

69
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:49,540
Miss Ying.

70
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:54,250
Three hundred years ago, thank you for risking your life multiple times to protect A-Deng.

71
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:55,409
This kindness,

72
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,330
I will never forget.

73
00:04:58,409 --> 00:04:59,940
I was protecting my sister.

74
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,410
It has nothing to do with you.
